{{Quote|The proud Qartheen shook off the yoke of unjust Kings long ago... so they are told at festivals by the Pureborn, the Kings' direct descendants who have control of the Thirteen ever since. Only now instead of scepters they use ships.|[[Xaro Xhoan Daxos]]|Qarth (Histories &amp; Lore)}}

The '''Pureborn''' are the descendants of the deposed [[King of Qarth|Kings]] of [[Qarth]]. Many Pureborn are [[merchants]] and members of [[the Thirteen]], the ruling council of the city, holding hereditary seats, which allows them to keep control over the city.
